verbose_text: As shown in Fig. XREF_FIG A, pretreatment of K1 cells with a general caspase inhibitor Z-VAD-FMK (50 muM) failed to reverse Obatoclax induced cell death, indicating that Obatoclax induced mixed forms of cell death in DTC cells other than Caspase related apoptosis.
evidence: cell death, indicating that Obatoclax induced mixed forms of cell death
